OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Fgood sunny spells in the morning
OL,7,Fbefore patches of cloud build up for a
OL,8,Ftime. Very warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry, warm and bright
OL,11,Fevening with some hazy sunny periods.
OL,12,FCloudier along the north coast, the
OL,13,Fcloud extending to all areas through
OL,14,Fthe night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FAnother warm or very warm
OL,17,Fday with sunny spells. Most places
OL,18,Fwill remain dry however there is the
OL,19,Frisk of a few afternoon showers in the
OL,20,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
